where she is?

723
00:43:34,520 --> 00:43:36,200
Okay, maybe I should ask Miss Prasad.
Miss Prasad!

724
00:43:36,280 --> 00:43:38,080
No, no, no. Mr. Sethi, please.

725
00:43:38,880 --> 00:43:40,040
- I'll tell you.
- What?

726
00:43:40,120 --> 00:43:42,800
- She's gone to meet a CITYone customer.
- Okay. Where?

727
00:43:42,880 --> 00:43:46,120
- Mr. Granger Woodruff.
- Okay. An American?

728
00:43:47,000 --> 00:43:48,920
- To America? Oh, my God!
- Oh, God. No...

729
00:43:48,960 --> 00:43:50,600
- I should have never let her work here.
- No.

730
00:43:50,680 --> 00:43:54,120
No, no, no! Mr. Sethi.
I promise you, she's coming back.

731
00:43:54,200 --> 00:43:57,000
