would impress Kit.

874
00:52:46,240 --> 00:52:49,080
- But the truth is, I think you're...
- Stupid.

875
00:52:50,200 --> 00:52:51,360
Right?

876
00:53:06,360 --> 00:53:08,720
Get into the car.
Both of you, get into the car.

877
00:53:08,760 --> 00:53:11,280
Rajiv! Rajiv, where are you off to?

878
00:53:11,400 --> 00:53:14,000
