to pick her up from the city.

879
00:53:14,040 --> 00:53:16,120
We didn't want to
inconvenience you, so...

880
00:53:16,200 --> 00:53:18,440
I'll also come with you, since you don't
know your way around here.

881
00:53:18,520 --> 00:53:20,840
No, no, we've got the map.
Show her the map.

882
00:53:20,920 --> 00:53:24,400
You've been already too generous, okay?
We'll return the car soon. Bye!

883
00:53:24,440 --> 00:53:25,440
- Bye!
- Bye!

884
00:53:39,560 --> 00:53:40,840
Who is it?

885
00:53:57,680 --> 00:53:59,920
