to eat your poisoned candy.

886
00:54:00,000 --> 00:54:01,360
It's just a little poison.

887
00:54:02,200 --> 00:54:04,120
Come on! Just one bite.

888
00:54:05,360 --> 00:54:06,880
Did you read it?

889
00:54:07,600 --> 00:54:09,080
No, I threw it away.

890
00:54:12,040 --> 00:54:14,200
