893
00:54:29,120 --> 00:54:31,080
Did you steal it from the hotel lobby?

894
00:54:31,160 --> 00:54:32,880
That is an outrageous accusation.

895
00:54:33,720 --> 00:54:35,560
Okay, yeah, I did.

896
00:54:45,160 --> 00:54:48,680
Okay, everything except the last thing.

897
00:54:52,440 --> 00:54:54,640
You're right. I'm sorry.

898
00:55:00,240 --> 00:55:03,400
At least let me give you a day
you'll never forget?

899
00:55:11,280 --> 00:55:13,560
All right, I promised you a day
you're never gonna forget,

900
00:55:13,640 --> 00:55:15,720
