- And your presentation?

901
00:55:15,760 --> 00:55:16,920
I'm procrastinating.

902
00:55:17,000 --> 00:55:19,880
Actually, I was hoping
you'd be my inspiration.

903
00:55:19,960 --> 00:55:21,200
Wow!

904
00:55:21,240 --> 00:55:23,240
Now, anything catches your eye,
just take a picture.

905
00:55:23,320 --> 00:55:24,360
Okay.

906
00:55:25,520 --> 00:55:28,800
