<i>Pretty woman</i>

909
00:55:34,960 --> 00:55:38,160
<i>I don't believe you, you're not the truth</i>

910
00:55:38,600 --> 00:55:41,960
<i>No one could look as good as you</i>

911
00:55:44,680 --> 00:55:45,960
<i>Mercy</i>

912
00:55:49,720 --> 00:55:51,440
<i>Pretty woman...</i>

913
00:55:51,480 --> 00:55:52,480
I don't know.

914
00:55:52,560 --> 00:55:55,120
Like hold the crab,
you need to get over your crab fear.

915
00:55:55,200 --> 00:55:56,240
Nibbling.

916
00:55:56,960 --> 00:55:59,240
<i>Pretty woman</i>

917
00:55:59,320 --> 00:56:03,240
<i>That you look lovely as can be</i>

918
00:56:03,320 --> 00:56:08,280
<i>Are you lonely just like me?</i>

919
00:56:09,120 --> 00:56:12,760
<i>Oh, oh, pretty woman</i>

920
00:56:16,320 --> 00:56:19,400
So, in India do your parents pick out
