and after like two days, it just dies?

930
00:56:47,360 --> 00:56:49,200
Better luck next life.

931
00:56:51,880 --> 00:56:53,200
Look at you.

932
00:56:54,400 --> 00:56:56,240
Probably find Priya under Granger.

933
00:56:58,000 --> 00:57:02,280
I mean, you know, the chances of you
finding your name are basically

934
00:57:02,320 --> 00:57:04,720
